snippet.title: Bunny Hop Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Kickstarter: https://BunnyHopGame.com
Bunny Hop is a challenging, yet simple, 2D platforming game that I'm developing for PC. It's my first PC game and a lot of my creative energy has went into this project lately. Any support is greatly appreciated! Thank you.
